RADIOBOX 

Description.

Radiobox is a GUI application, which should make it possible to control DBOX only using LCD Display Without TV.  At the moment radiobox dedicated to playing mp3 files from the network and shoutcast streams from internet.

Features.

Hierarchical menu.
Generating playlists from directories.
Playing mp3 files in random/normal order 
Playing shoutcast streams.
Flash memory reading/writting.




